{
  "openapi": "3.0.1",
  "info": {
    "title": "图片创建",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "description": "本文介绍图片创建 API 的请求与响应参数，与火山引擎模型方舟上游接口保持一致。\n\n统一入口为 `/byteplus/api/v3/images/generations`，支持 `seedream-5-0-260128`、`seedream-4-5-251128`、`seedream-4-0-250828` 等模型。各模型支持的参数存在差异，详见各字段说明中的模型兼容性备注。",
    "license": {
      "name": "Project License",
      "url": "https://github.com/QuantumNous/new-api/blob/main/LICENSE"
    }
  },
  "servers": [
    {
      "url": "https://baze-api.powerbuyin.top",
      "description": "Baze API 服务地址"
    }
  ],
  "tags": [
    {
      "name": "Seedream API Compat",
      "description": "Seedream 图片创建接口"
    }
  ],
  "paths": {
    "/byteplus/api/v3/images/generations": {
      "post": {
        "summary": "图片创建",
        "description": "调用图片生成模型，根据文本提示词生成图像。支持文生图、图生图、多图融合、批量序列生成等模式。\n\n各模型支持的参数存在差异：\n- **Seedream 5.0 lite**：支持 `prompt`、`image`（string/array）、`image2`–`image10`、`size`（2K/3K 或自定义像素）、`output_format`（png/jpeg）、`response_format`、`watermark`、`stream`、`sequential_image_generation`、`sequential_image_generation_options`、`tools`（web_search）、`optimize_prompt_options`（仅 standard）、`provider`\n- **Seedream 4.5**：支持 `prompt`、`image`、`image2`–`image10`、`size`（2K/4K 或自定义像素）、`width`、`height`、`scale`、`force_single`、`min_ratio`、`max_ratio`、`optimize_prompt_options`（仅 standard）、`watermark`、`provider`\n- **Seedream 4.0**：支持 `prompt`、`image`、`image2`–`image10`、`size`（1K/2K/4K 或自定义像素）、`width`、`height`、`scale`、`force_single`、`min_ratio`、`max_ratio`、`optimize_prompt_options`（standard/fast）、`watermark`、`provider`",
        "operationId": "seedreamImageCreate",
        "tags": [
          "Seedream API Compat"
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ImageCreateRequest"
              },
              "examples": {
                "text_to_image_5_0_lite": {
                  "summary": "文生图 — Seedream 5.0 lite",
                  "value": {
                    "model": "seedream-5-0-260128",
                    "prompt": "充满活力的特写编辑肖像，模特眼神犀利，头戴雕塑感帽子，色彩拼接丰富，具有 Vogue 杂志封面的美学风格，中画幅拍摄，工作室灯光强烈。",
                    "size": "2K",
                    "output_format": "png",
                    "watermark": false
                  }
                },
                "image_to_image_5_0_lite": {
                  "summary": "图生图 — Seedream 5.0 lite 单图参考",
                  "value": {
                    "model": "seedream-5-0-260128",
                    "prompt": "保持模特姿势和液态服装的流动形状不变，将服装材质从银色金属改为完全透明的清水（或玻璃），光影从反射变为折射。",
                    "image": "https://example.com/reference.png",
                    "size": "2K",
                    "output_format": "png",
                    "watermark": false
                  }
                },
                "multi_image_fusion_5_0_lite": {
                  "summary": "多图融合 — Seedream 5.0 lite",
                  "value": {
                    "model": "seedream-5-0-260128",
                    "prompt": "将图1 的服装换为图2 的服装",
                    "image": [
                      "https://example.com/photo1.png",
                      "https://example.com/photo2.png"
                    ],
                    "sequential_image_generation": "disabled",
                    "size": "2K",
                    "output_format": "png",
                    "watermark": false
                  }
                },
                "sequential_images_5_0_lite": {
                  "summary": "文生组图 — Seedream 5.0 lite",
                  "value": {
                    "model": "seedream-5-0-260128",
                    "prompt": "生成一组共 4 张连贯插画，核心为同一庭院一角的四季变迁，以统一风格展现四季独特色彩、元素与氛围",
                    "size": "2K",
                    "sequential_image_generation": "auto",
                    "sequential_image_generation_options": {
                      "max_images": 4
                    },
                    "stream": false,
                    "output_format": "png",
                    "response_format": "url",
                    "watermark": false
                  }
                },
                "web_search_5_0_lite": {
                  "summary": "联网搜索 — Seedream 5.0 lite",
                  "value": {
                    "model": "seedream-5-0-260128",
                    "prompt": "制作一张上海未来 5 日的天气预报图，采用现代扁平化插画风格，清晰展示每日天气、温度和穿搭建议。",
                    "size": "2048x2048",
                    "tools": [
                      {
                        "type": "web_search"
                      }
                    ],
                    "output_format": "png",
                    "response_format": "url",
                    "watermark": false
                  }
                },
                "text_to_image_4_0": {
                  "summary": "文生图 — Seedream 4.0",
                  "value": {
                    "model": "seedream-4-0-250828",
                    "prompt": "一只可爱的猫咪在花园里玩耍，阳光明媚",
                    "size": "2K",
                    "scale": 0.5,
                    "force_single": false,
                    "optimize_prompt_options": {
                      "mode": "standard"
                    }
                  }
                },
                "image_to_image_4_0": {
                  "summary": "图生图 — Seedream 4.0",
                  "value": {
                    "model": "seedream-4-0-250828",
                    "prompt": "背景换成演唱会现场",
                    "image": "https://example.com/reference-image.jpg",
                    "scale": 0.6,
                    "width": 2048,
                    "height": 2048,
                    "optimize_prompt_options": {
                      "mode": "fast"
                    }
                  }
                },
                "text_to_image_4_5": {
                  "summary": "文生图 — Seedream 4.5",
                  "value": {
                    "model": "seedream-4-5-251128",
                    "prompt": "一只可爱的猫咪在花园里玩耍，阳光明媚",
                    "size": "2K",
                    "scale": 0.5,
                    "force_single": false,
                    "optimize_prompt_options": {
                      "mode": "standard"
                    }
                  }
                },
                "image_to_image_4_5": {
                  "summary": "图生图 — Seedream 4.5",
                  "value": {
                    "model": "seedream-4-5-251128",
                    "prompt": "背景换成演唱会现场",
                    "image": "https://example.com/reference-image.jpg",
                    "scale": 0.6,
                    "width": 2048,
                    "height": 2048,
                    "optimize_prompt_options": {
                      "mode": "standard"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "调用成功，返回图像生成结果。",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ImageCreateResponse"
                },
                "examples": {
                  "single_image_url": {
                    "summary": "单图 — URL 格式",
                    "value": {
                      "created": 1736123456,
                      "data": [
                        {
                          "url": "https://example.com/generated-image-1.jpg"
                        }
                      ],
                      "usage": {
                        "total_tokens": 0,
                        "input_tokens": 0,
                        "output_tokens": 0,
                        "input_tokens_details": {
                          "text_tokens": 0,
                          "image_tokens": 0
                        },
                        "image_count": 1
                      },
                      "provider": "火山方舟",
                      "model": "seedream-4-0-250828"
                    }
                  },
                  "single_image_b64": {
                    "summary": "单图 — Base64 格式",
                    "value": {
                      "created": 1736123456,
                      "data": [
                        {
                          "b64_json": "iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAA..."
                        }
                      ],
                      "usage": {
                        "total_tokens": 0,
                        "input_tokens": 0,
                        "output_tokens": 0,
                        "input_tokens_details": {
                          "text_tokens": 0,
                          "image_tokens": 0
                        },
                        "image_count": 1
                      },
                      "provider": "火山方舟",
                      "model": "seedream-5-0-260128"
                    }
                  },
                  "multi_image": {
                    "summary": "多图输出",
                    "value": {
                      "created": 1736123456,
                      "data": [
                        {
                          "url": "https://example.com/generated-image-1.jpg",
                          "b64_json": "iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAA..."
                        },
                        {
                          "url": "https://example.com/generated-image-2.jpg"
                        }
                      ],
                      "usage": {
                        "total_tokens": 0,
                        "input_tokens": 0,
                        "output_tokens": 0,
                        "input_tokens_details": {
                          "text_tokens": 0,
                          "image_tokens": 0
                        },
                        "image_count": 2
                      },
                      "provider": "火山方舟",
                      "model": "seedream-4-0-250828"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "请求参数不合法。",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"
                },
                "examples": {
                  "invalid_request": {
                    "summary": "参数错误",
                    "value": {
                      "error": {
                        "message": "请求体格式错误或字段取值非法",
                        "type": "invalid_request_error",
                        "code": "bad_request_body",
                        "param": ""
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "鉴权失败，例如未提供令牌或令牌无效。",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"
                },
                "examples": {
                  "unauthorized": {
                    "summary": "未授权",
                    "value": {
                      "error": {
                        "message": "无效的令牌",
                        "type": "api_error",
                        "code": "access_denied",
                        "param": ""
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "429": {
            "description": "触发速率限制或账户额度不足。",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"
                },
                "examples": {
                  "quota_exceeded": {
                    "summary": "额度不足或速率受限",
                    "value": {
                      "error": {
                        "message": "当前账户额度不足，请稍后重试",
                        "type": "api_error",
                        "code": "insufficient_user_quota",
                        "param": ""
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "500": {
            "description": "服务端处理请求时发生内部错误。",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"
                },
                "examples": {
                  "internal_error": {
                    "summary": "内部处理失败",
                    "value": {
                      "error": {
                        "message": "服务内部处理失败，请稍后重试",
                        "type": "api_error",
                        "code": "gen_relay_info_failed",
                        "param": ""
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "security": [
          {
            "BearerAuth": []
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  },
  "components": {
    "securitySchemes": {
      "BearerAuth": {
        "type": "http",
        "scheme": "bearer",
        "bearerFormat": "JWT",
        "description": "在请求头中传入 `Authorization: Bearer <token>`。"
      }
    },
    "schemas": {
      "ImageCreateRequest": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "model",
          "prompt"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "model": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "图像生成模型名称。支持的模型：\n\n- `seedream-5-0-260128`（Seedream 5.0 lite，最新，推荐）\n- `seedream-4-5-251128`（Seedream 4.5，支持 4K 与强文本渲染）\n- `seedream-4-0-250828`（Seedream 4.0，维护状态，最经济的 4K 选项）",
            "example": "seedream-5-0-260128"
          },
          "prompt": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "用于生成图像的提示词，中英文均可。建议用简洁连贯的自然语言写明**主体 + 行为 + 环境**，可补充风格、色彩、光影、构图等。\n\n- 建议不超过 300 个汉字或 600 个英文单词，字数过多容易信息分散，模型可能因此忽略细节\n- 最长不超过 800 字符\n- 除 `\"\"` 外不建议输入特殊符号如 `$`\n- 支持 `prompt` 中直接指定生图比例，模型会根据 `size` 字段智能判断生图宽高比",
            "example": "一只可爱的柯基犬在草地上奔跑，阳光明媚，写实风格"
          },
          "image": {
            "oneOf": [
              {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "单张参考图 URL 或 Base64 编码字符串。"
              },
              {
                "type": "array",
                "description": "多张参考图 URL 或 Base64 编码数组，最多 10 张。",
                "items": {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                "maxItems": 10
              }
            ],
            "description": "第一张参考图像，用于图生图/多图融合。支持 URL 或 Base64 编码。\n\n**URL 格式**：`http://` 或 `https://` 开头的链接\n\n**Base64 格式**：带 `data:image/{format};base64,` 前缀或不带前缀均可，支持 PNG、JPEG、JPG 等格式\n\n**数组格式示例**：`[\"url1\", \"url2\", ...]`\n\n**多图输入说明**：支持最多 10 张图，可通过 `image` 数组格式传入，或通过 `image`、`image2`、`image3`…`image10` 等参数分别传入\n\n**图片限制**：\n- 图片格式：JPEG、PNG、WEBP、BMP、TIFF、GIF\n- 图片文件大小：不超过 10 MB\n- 总像素 ≤ 6000×6000\n- 输入图宽高比范围：[1/16, 16]（Seedream 5.0 lite）/ [1/3, 3]（Seedream 4.0/4.5）"
          },
          "image2": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "第二张参考图像（多图融合时使用）。格式要求同 `image` 参数。"
          },
          "image3": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "第三张参考图像。格式要求同 `image` 参数。"
          },
          "image4": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "第四张参考图像。格式要求同 `image` 参数。"
          },
          "image5": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "第五张参考图像。格式要求同 `image` 参数。"
          },
          "image6": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "第六张参考图像。格式要求同 `image` 参数。"
          },
          "image7": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "第七张参考图像。格式要求同 `image` 参数。"
          },
          "image8": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "第八张参考图像。格式要求同 `image` 参数。"
          },
          "image9": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "第九张参考图像。格式要求同 `image` 参数。"
          },
          "image10": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "第十张参考图像（多图融合时使用）。格式要求同 `image` 参数。"
          },
          "size": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "输出图像尺寸。支持两种方式（不可混用）：\n\n**方式一**：分辨率关键词，并在 prompt 中描述宽高比/形状/用途，由模型判断具体像素。\n\n| 模型 | 支持分辨率 |\n|------|------------|\n| seedream-5-0-260128 | `2K`、`3K` |\n| seedream-4-5-251128 | `2K`、`4K` |\n| seedream-4-0-250828 | `1K`、`2K`、`4K` |\n\n**方式二**：直接指定宽高像素值，如 `\"2048x2048\"`。总像素需满足模型版本对应的范围要求，宽高比 ∈ [1/16, 16]。\n\n| 模型 | 总像素范围 |\n|------|------------|\n| seedream-5-0-260128 | [3686400, 10404496] |\n| seedream-4-5-251128 | [3686400, 16777216] |\n| seedream-4-0-250828 | [921600, 16777216] |",
            "default": "2048x2048",
            "example": "2048x2048"
          },
          "width": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "生成图像宽度，需同时传 `width` 和 `height` 才会生效。\n\n- Seedream 4.0：宽高乘积在 [1048576, 16777216]，宽高比在 [`min_ratio`, `max_ratio`] 之间\n- Seedream 4.5：宽高乘积在 [1048576, 16777216]，宽高比在 [`min_ratio`, `max_ratio`] 之间\n- Seedream 5.0 lite 不支持此参数",
            "example": 2048
          },
          "height": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "生成图像高度，需同时传 `width` 和 `height` 才会生效。\n\n- Seedream 4.0：宽高乘积在 [1048576, 16777216]，宽高比在 [`min_ratio`, `max_ratio`] 之间\n- Seedream 4.5：宽高乘积在 [1048576, 16777216]，宽高比在 [`min_ratio`, `max_ratio`] 之间\n- Seedream 5.0 lite 不支持此参数",
            "example": 2048
          },
          "scale": {
            "type": "number",
            "description": "文本描述影响的程度，该值越大代表文本描述影响程度越大，且输入图片影响程度越小。\n\n- 仅 Seedream 4.0 和 4.5 支持此参数\n- Seedream 5.0 lite 不支持此参数",
            "default": 0.5,
            "minimum": 0,
            "maximum": 1,
            "example": 0.5
          },
          "force_single": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "description": "是否强制生成单图。若对延迟&价格敏感，建议使用该参数。\n\n- 仅 Seedream 4.0 和 4.5 支持此参数\n- Seedream 5.0 lite 不支持此参数\n\n注意：生成的组图越多，耗时越久，且生成耗时会随图片数量增多而显著变长。",
            "default": false
          },
          "min_ratio": {
            "type": "number",
            "description": "生图结果的宽/高 ≥ `min_ratio`，如果智能选比例 < `min_ratio`，则用 `min_ratio`。\n\n- 仅 Seedream 4.0 和 4.5 支持此参数\n- Seedream 5.0 lite 不支持此参数",
            "default": 0.333,
            "minimum": 0.0625,
            "example": 0.333
          },
          "max_ratio": {
            "type": "number",
            "description": "生图结果的宽/高 ≤ `max_ratio`，如果智能选比例 > `max_ratio`，则用 `max_ratio`。\n\n- 仅 Seedream 4.0 和 4.5 支持此参数\n- Seedream 5.0 lite 不支持此参数",
            "default": 3,
            "maximum": 16,
            "example": 3
          },
          "output_format": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "jpeg",
              "png"
            ],
            "description": "生成图片的文件格式。\n\n- Seedream 5.0 lite 支持 `png` 和 `jpeg`\n- Seedream 4.0 和 4.5 仅支持 `jpeg`",
            "default": "png"
          },
          "response_format": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "url",
              "b64_json"
            ],
            "description": "图片在 API 响应中的返回方式。\n\n- `url`：返回图片下载链接（24 小时有效）\n- `b64_json`：直接返回 Base64 编码的图片数据",
            "default": "url"
          },
          "stream": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "description": "是否开启流式输出。设为 `true` 后，模型每生成一张图片即通过 SSE 推送，可改善等待体验。\n\n- 仅 Seedream 5.0 lite、Seedream 4.5 和 Seedream 4.0 支持流式响应\n- 详见「流式响应」文档",
            "default": false
          },
          "sequential_image_generation": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "auto",
              "disabled"
            ],
            "description": "批量序列生成开关。\n\n- `auto`：根据 prompt 自动生成一组内容关联的图片\n- `disabled`：仅生成单张图片\n\n当前支持的 Seedream 模型均可使用该能力。",
            "default": "disabled"
          },
          "sequential_image_generation_options": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "批量序列生成配置，仅在 `sequential_image_generation` 为 `auto` 时生效。",
            "x-valid-when": {
              "sequential_image_generation": [
                "auto"
              ]
            },
            "properties": {
              "max_images": {
                "type": "integer",
                "description": "本次请求最多允许生成的图片数量。取值范围 1–15。实际生成数量还需满足：输入参考图数 + 生成图数 ≤ 15。",
                "minimum": 1,
                "maximum": 15,
                "default": 15
              }
            }
          },
          "watermark": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "description": "是否在生成的图片中添加水印。\n\n- `true`：在图片右下角添加「AI 生成」字样的水印标识\n- `false`：不添加水印",
            "default": true
          },
          "tools": {
            "type": "array",
            "description": "扩展能力配置。仅 Seedream 5.0 lite 支持此参数。\n\n- 传入 `[{ \"type\": \"web_search\" }]` 可开启联网搜索，按需搜索互联网提升时效性（如天气、商品等），但会增加时延\n- Seedream 4.0 和 4.5 不支持此参数",
            "items": {
              "type": "object",
              "properties": {
                "type": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "enum": [
                    "web_search"
                  ],
                  "description": "扩展能力类型。`web_search` 表示联网搜索。"
                }
              },
              "required": [
                "type"
              ]
            },
            "example": "[{ \"type\": \"web_search\" }]"
          },
          "optimize_prompt_options": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "提示词优化功能配置。\n\n| 模型 | 支持模式 |\n|------|----------|\n| seedream-5-0-260128 | 仅 `standard` |\n| seedream-4-5-251128 | 仅 `standard`（仅支持标准模式） |\n| seedream-4-0-250828 | `standard` 和 `fast` |",
            "properties": {
              "mode": {
                "type": "string",
                "enum": [
                  "standard",
                  "fast"
                ],
                "description": "提示词优化模式。\n\n- `standard`：标准模式，生成内容的质量更高，耗时较长\n- `fast`：快速模式，生成内容的耗时更短，质量一般\n\n注意：Seedream 5.0 lite 和 4.5 仅支持 `standard` 模式，Seedream 4.0 支持 `standard` 和 `fast`。",
                "default": "standard"
              }
            }
          },
          "provider": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "调度配置参数。对象类型，包含图像生成特有参数和服务商调度参数。",
            "properties": {
              "enable_image_base64": {
                "type": "boolean",
                "description": "是否在响应数据的 `data` 字段中同时返回图像的 Base64 编码。默认 `false`。",
                "default": false
              },
              "enable_image_origin_data": {
                "type": "boolean",
                "description": "是否在响应中包含原始响应数据。默认 `false`。",
                "default": false
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "ImageCreateResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "created": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64",
            "description": "响应创建时间，Unix 时间戳（秒）。"
          },
          "data": {
            "type": "array",
            "description": "生成的图像数据数组。批量序列生成场景下可能包含多张图片。",
            "items": {
              "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ImageData"
            }
          },
          "usage": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "使用情况统计。",
            "properties": {
              "total_tokens": {
                "type": "integer",
                "description": "总 token 数。图像生成场景通常为 0。"
              },
              "input_tokens": {
                "type": "integer",
                "description": "输入 token 数。图像生成场景通常为 0。"
              },
              "output_tokens": {
                "type": "integer",
                "description": "输出 token 数。图像生成场景通常为 0。"
              },
              "input_tokens_details": {
                "type": "object",
                "description": "输入 token 详情。",
                "properties": {
                  "text_tokens": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "description": "文本 token 数。图像生成场景通常为 0。"
                  },
                  "image_tokens": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "description": "图像 token 数。图像生成场景通常为 0。"
                  }
                }
              },
              "image_count": {
                "type": "integer",
                "description": "生成的图像数量。"
              }
            }
          },
          "provider": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "服务商名称。"
          },
          "model": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "模型名称。"
          },
          "origin_data": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "服务商的原始响应数据。仅在请求参数 `provider.enable_image_origin_data` 设置为 `true` 时返回此字段。默认不返回。"
          }
        }
      },
      "ImageData": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "url": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "图片下载链接。`response_format` 为 `url` 时返回，链接 24 小时内有效，请及时保存。"
          },
          "b64_json": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "图片 Base64 编码数据。仅在 `response_format` 为 `b64_json` 或请求参数 `provider.enable_image_base64` 为 `true` 时返回。不带 `data:image/...;base64,` 前缀。"
          },
          "size": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "图像尺寸（宽x高），如 `\"2048x2048\"`。仅 Seedream 5.0 lite、4.5、4.0 返回此字段。"
          }
        }
      },
      "ErrorResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "error": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "message": {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "错误描述信息。"
              },
              "type": {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "错误类型。"
              },
              "code": {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "错误码。"
              },
              "param": {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "触发错误的参数名。"
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}